<h2 style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">Clock Model</h2>

<div style="line-height:2">
<p style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">The Clock Model can teach the children about the concept of time. Introduce the features of analogue clock by turning on the hour hand and minute hand. Drag the clock hands to teach the children to read the time.</p>

<p style="font-family:verdana; color:#333">Turn the 5-minute interval on to make the minutes marked on an outer ring visible. The time shown on the analogue clock will be displayed in the digital clock. Use the plus (+) and minus (-) sign to control the hour hand and minute hand.</p>
</div>